snippet.title: Unrooted - Official Release Date Trailer | OTK Games Expo 2024
snippet.description: Dive into the vibrant world and gameplay of Unrooted in this latest trailer for the upcoming precision platformer game. Unrooted will be available on PC on August 2, 2024. In Unrooted, take up your courage and squash your fear of heights. Travel upwards to lands no sapling has dared to explore before. But heed with caution, the higher you journey, the more you risk.
